       Added version="1.1" to dashboards to address jquery upgrade.

       1.0.0 Feb 28, 2019
       --------
       First release.

Using this App
----------------------------
Configuration: Install app on a search head. Configure AWS to publish SES events to Kinesis Firehose with a data stream pointing to your Splunk HEC, configured with a sourcetype of aws:ses.
